{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🛑 NodeInterrupt 深度解析\n",
    "\n",
    "> **`interrupt_before` = "到这里统一停车。"**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **`NodeInterrupt` = "node 根据现场情况，主动踩刹车。"**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 一、先回顾 `interrupt_before`（静态 interrupt）\n",
    "\n",
    "你已经学过的："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 静态 interrupt - compile 时就决定好了\n",
    "# graph = builder.compile(\n",
    "#     interrupt_before=[\"tools\"]\n",
    "# )"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "意思：graph 运行之前就说好了 → **每次到 tools 前，都停。**\n",
    "\n",
    "像高速收费站：每辆车都要停，不管什么情况。\n",
    "\n",
    "这是 **静态 interrupt**，提前配置。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 二、NodeInterrupt 是什么？（动态 interrupt）\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeInterrupt 完全不同：\n",
    "- 不是 compile 时决定\n",
    "- 是 **node 自己在 runtime 决定**\n",
    "\n",
    "像 node 内部说：\"等一下，这个情况不对，我先暂停。\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from langgraph.errors import NodeInterrupt\n",
    "\n",
    "def payment_node(state):\n",
    "    amount = state[\"amount\"]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if amount > 10000:\n",
    "        raise NodeInterrupt(\n",
    "            \"Large payment requires approval\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return state"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "流程：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "payment node → 检查金额 → 超过一万 → raise NodeInterrupt → 暂停\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "不是 graph 提前规定，是 **node 临场判断**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 三、为什么需要 NodeInterrupt？\n",
    "\n",
    "现实 agent 里，不是所有情况都需要人工介入，只有 **某些特殊条件**：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 场景 | 条件 | 暂停原因 |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| 🚀 部署生产环境 | `if env == \"prod\"` | "确认部署吗？" |\n",
    "| 📧 发邮件 | `if recipient_count > 1000` | "确认群发吗？" |\n",
    "| 💰 花钱 | `if cost > $500` | "确认购买吗？" |\n",
    "| 🗑️ 删除文件 | `if delete_count > 100` | "确认删除吗？" |\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeInterrupt 本质：**conditional human-in-the-loop**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 四、本质区别对比表\n",
    "\n",
    "| | `interrupt_before` | `NodeInterrupt` |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| 谁决定停？ | graph | node |\n",
    "| 什么时候决定？ | compile time | runtime |\n",
    "| 是否看数据？ | 不看 | 看 state |\n",
    "| 灵活性 | 固定 | 很高 |\n",
    "\n",
    "**interrupt_before 例子：**\n",
    "```text\n",
    "$1 → 停 | $10 → 停 | $100 → 停 | $10000 → 停（全停）\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**NodeInterrupt 例子：**\n",
    "```text\n",
    "$1 → 继续 | $10 → 继续 | $100 → 继续 | $10000 → 停（更智能）\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 五、NodeInterrupt 发生后，内部发生了什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "假设 `thread_id=\"1\"`，运行过程：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "step1: START\n",
    "step2: assistant → checkpoint 保存\n",
    "step3: 进入 payment_node → raise NodeInterrupt(...)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "LangGraph 会：\n",
    "1. **保存 checkpoint**（如 `checkpoint_3`）\n",
    "2. **保存 interrupt metadata**（如 `{\"reason\": \"Large payment\"}`）\n",
    "3. **thread 保持 alive**（thread 不会结束）\n",
    "\n",
    "所以你可以 later resume。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 六、Resume 怎么工作？\n",
    "\n",
    "暂停后 → 人工审批（UI / Slack）→ 继续："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from langgraph.types import Command\n",
    "\n",
    "# 从上次 checkpoint 接着跑（不是重跑）\n",
    "# graph.stream(\n",
    "#     Command(resume=True),\n",
    "#     config\n",
    "# )"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "流程：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "checkpoint 3 → resume → payment node 后面继续\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 七、NodeInterrupt 和 Thread 的关系 🔗\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeInterrupt **必须依赖 thread + checkpoint**，否则恢复不了。\n",
    "\n",
    "因为暂停时，LangGraph 必须知道："哪条 timeline 停住了？"\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "thread 1: paused ⏸️\n",
    "thread 2: running ▶️\n",
    "thread 3: finished ✅\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeInterrupt 和 thread 是 **强绑定**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 八、NodeInterrupt 和 Super Step 的关系\n",
    "\n",
    "如果 node 在某个 super step 里 interrupt，**整个 super step 会暂停**。\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "A → B,C (parallel) → D\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "如果 B 里 `raise NodeInterrupt()`：\n",
    "- super step 2 暂停\n",
    "- checkpoint 保存\n",
    "- 等待 resume\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeInterrupt 不是"小异常"，它会影响 **整个 graph scheduling**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 九、实用场景：Bug-Fix Agent 🐛\n",
    "\n",
    "结合 Playwright agent："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 在 deploy node 中使用 NodeInterrupt\n",
    "def deploy_node(state):\n",
    "    if state[\"branch\"] == \"main\":\n",
    "        raise NodeInterrupt(\n",
    "            \"Deploying to main branch - requires approval\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    # ... 继续部署"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "然后 Slack 通知 → 你点 Approve → 继续部署。\n",
    "\n",
    "这就是非常典型的 production 用法。✅"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 💡 一句话记忆\n",
    "\n",
    "> **`interrupt_before` = "到这里统一停车。"** 🚧\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **`NodeInterrupt` = "node 根据现场情况，主动踩刹车。"** 🛑\n",
    "\n",
    "如果你看到 `Command(resume=...)`、`graph.get_state(config)`、`state.tasks` 这些东西，\n",
    "那就是在围绕 `NodeInterrupt` 这套暂停/恢复机制展开。"
   ]
  }
 ],
